description: Nilar International AB is a SE-based company operating in Electrical Equipment industry. The company is headquartered in Taby, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2021-04-30. Nilar International AB is a Sweden-based manufacturer of storage batteries. The firm consists of only one reportable segment Nilar. which r operates in the energy storage market and with special focus on three segments: home and small-scale storage, smart grid infrastructure, and commercial and industrial support.
